363
00:32:55,727 --> 00:32:57,371
...es zona protegida...

364
00:32:57,395 --> 00:32:58,782
...así que si quisieran talar...

365
00:32:58,806 --> 00:33:00,130
...matarlos sería--

366
00:33:01,032 --> 00:33:02,409
<i>Teníamos que enfrentarlos,
