450
00:36:44,822 --> 00:36:46,433
<i>Lucha por volverse a parar.

451
00:36:46,457 --> 00:36:48,101
<i>Sí.

452
00:36:48,125 --> 00:36:49,870
<i>¡Oh, llegó la hora de sufrir!

